<section>
  <title>Print Options</title>
  <para>To edit a pending sale select edit to under Sale tab . The following
  screen will appear:</para>
  <mediaobject>
    <imageobject>
      <imagedata fileref="images/printOptions.png" />
    </imageobject>
    <caption>Print Options</caption>
  </mediaobject>
  <para>When creating a new sale or processing a pending sale, you are
  presented with the following options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Print Automatically</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Always use this printer</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
  <para>At the top of and to the far right of the screen, the following
  buttons are available:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>OK</term>
      <listitem>
        <para></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>CANCEL</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Closes the screen without creating a new retail sale, returning
        you to the application desktop.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>
